tagline: A jQuery plugin. Return world countries name as option tag
body:
jQuery populateCountry plugin

it only do one thing - return options tag contains world countries name


Usage: 
$("select#id").populateCountry();
or
$("select.class").populateCountry();
name: Jquery-populatecountry
